Booking - Class in model
This Model class contains all information of a booking - including the name of the moviegoer, the email address, the date and time, the cineplex name, the cinema ID, the movie name, the seat booked, the price of the ticket, the age of the person, and the ticket ID.
Booking() - Constructor for class model.Booking
Constructor to be used when showing no booking has been done All attributes are set to null for string or 0 for int
Booking(String[]) - Constructor for class model.Booking
Constructor strictly used for converting the attributes of the booking database into model attributes
Booking(String, String, String, String, int, String, String, double, int, String) - Constructor for class model.Booking
Constructor used for booking a ticket
Booking(String, String, Date, String, int, String, String, double, int, String) - Constructor for class model.Booking
Constructor used for booking a ticket
booking_insert_actual(Booking[]) - Method in class controller.MovieBookingController
method to insert an array of bookings into database, the method will traverse through the array and insert each booking into the booking database as well as update seating plan for that showtime
bookTicket(String, String, Date, String, int, String, int, int, double, int, String) - Method in class controller.MovieBookingController
Method to check whether a booking can be inserted, makes sure that seats are available, and age requirement is met
